name: Des-Colagem III
description:
“Ungluing III", collage on A-4 size cardboard.
Once I finish the collage, I let it dry and peel off whatever is possible, achieving unpredictable results through ungluing. 
Cirlei Gonçalves is a designer, visual artist, clothing and accessories customizer and artisan. She lives and works in Curitiba/PR - Brazil
